data.name: NonVirtualSetupSpecificationDescription

data.value: Member {0} can not be intercepted. Only interface members and virtual, overriding, and abstract members can be intercepted.

data.name: UnusedReceivedDescription
data.value: Unused received check.
data.comment: An optional longer localizable description of the diagnostic.

data.name: UnusedReceivedMessageFormat
data.value: Unused received check. To fix, make sure there is a call after "{0}". Correct: "sub.{0}().SomeCall();". Incorrect: "sub.{0}();"
data.comment: The format-able message the diagnostic displays.

data.name: UnusedReceivedTitle
data.value: Received check.
data.comment: The title of the diagnostic.
